{"tid":1850116,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎》丹麥百年大報刊登「五星病毒旗」諷刺漫畫 中國氣炸","createTime":"2020-01-29T11:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T09:29:22.000Z","uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd223e64ea6b17386241fc14990193586daef1c","tid":1850116,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:21:11.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎》丹麥百年大報刊登「五星病毒旗」諷刺漫畫 中國氣炸<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕「2019新型冠狀病毒」（2019-nCoV，下稱武漢肺炎）疫情持續延燒，死亡人數已達106人。丹麥媒體近日在網站上發布一張諷刺畫作，將中國五星旗上的五星改為病毒圖樣。中國駐丹麥使館痛批「嚴重傷害中國人民感情」，要求報社和投稿者公開道歉。<br />\n<br />\n1871年創辦的《日德蘭郵報》為丹麥主流媒體之一，該報昨日在網站上發布的一則名為「冠狀病毒」的投稿漫畫，將中國五星旗的五星畫為病毒圖案，諷刺意味明顯，且瀏覽數衝到該網站第一名。報方在網頁內附上免責聲明，指作品為藝術家的態度、觀點表達，可能與《日德蘭郵報》立場不同。<br />\n<br />\n此舉無疑惹怒中國，中國駐丹麥大使館聲明表示，中國政府和人民正全力應對疫情，國際社會也表達極大同情、關心和支持，《日德蘭郵報》卻刊載辱華漫畫，痛批「毫無基本同情和同理心，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>嚴重傷害中國人民感情</strong></span>」，對此表達強烈憤慨，要求報方和作者公開向中國人民道歉。<br />\n<br />\n《日德蘭郵報》的漫畫專欄在2005年，就因刊載諷刺伊斯蘭教先知穆罕默德的12幅漫畫，引發穆斯林強烈不滿，官方則以捍衛言論自由為由站穩立場，進而衍生出一連串國際暴力事件。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpKYgFsz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpKYgFsz.jpg&h=9c5d1583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續擴大。（法新社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpN4exnx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpN4exnx.jpg&h=06736267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《日德蘭郵報》刊登武漢肺炎諷刺漫畫。（圖片擷取自《日德蘭郵報》網站）"},{"pid":"48c1d118025805cfba23f01376017ef63eadaaea","tid":1850116,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"病毒國國徽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiNTcg4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiNTcg4.jpg&h=a5f4c663&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6585d77dacca8a8a5461a8bef45a95acdc93e55","tid":1850116,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48c1d118025805cfba23f01376017ef63eadaaea","tid":1850116,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"病毒國國徽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiNTcg4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiNTcg4.jpg&h=a5f4c663&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"外圍個圈都應該變埋病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bbb7585d24d04c0ce5f84cee8e1f06a895ffe8","tid":1850116,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nE7o9ok.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnE7o9ok.gif&h=e2a82b9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d452d9421d92a9b02ce1213add56af1cce1221a8","tid":1850116,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:29:22.000Z","msg":"花10秒支持丹麥廣播公司企硬，不向大陸病毒國家道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dr.dk/nyheder/indland/ambassadoer-fastholder-krav-om-undskyldning-jp-tegning-hjerteloest-og-egoistisk?from=groupmessage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dr.dk%2Fnyheder%2Findland%2Fambassadoer-fastholder-krav-om-undskyldning-jp-tegning-hjerteloest-og-egoistisk%3Ffrom%3Dgroupmessage&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH063eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=59fe3c9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dr.dk/nyheder/indland/ambassadoer-fastholder-krav-om-undskyldning-jp-tegning-hjerteloest-og-egoistisk?from=groupmessage</a><br />\n<br />\n碌落去少少，就見到病毒國旗和以下問題<br />\nB&oslash;r Jyllands-Posten og tegneren undskylde til Kina for tegningen?<br />\n<br />\n投Nej (不用道歉)"}]}